node.text: Cried buckets watching it 😭 May Allah grants them syifa soon 🙏

Wow, what a session it was chatting with two Covid19 patients.
.
Theres so much for us to learn. Watch as they share their experiences and the struggles they are going thru.
.
One of them is warded together with her one year old as both of them are Covid19 positive 😭
.
The other patient has been away from her 2yrs old son for more than 1 month!
.
Snippets here and you can watch the full video at @aanurul’s
.
Lets pray that they will recover soon and go home to their loved ones, shall we?
.
#stayhomesg #spreadlove
Cried buckets watching it 😭 May Allah grants them syifa soon 🙏
